we used and shared it on Kaggle.

Spotipy authentication instructions 
-----------------------------------

Install spotipy: 
  pip install spotipy

To be able to use the spotipy library, you will need:
  A spotify account
  A spotify developer account

Once logged in to your spotify developer account, 
obtain the following authentication tokens:
  spotifyclientid 
  spotifyclientsecret

Add the following lines to your bash profile:
  export SPOTIFY_CLIENT_ID=yourspotifyclientid
  export SPOTIFY_CLIENT_SECRET=yourspotifyclientsecret



